node.text:
I’m so excited to share this sneak peek of my new short program! Looking forward to performing this for a live audience this season!! 😄

Big thanks to @oniceperspectives for his awesome camera work. Filming this was so much fun. 

Music: Restrictus by Mario Batkovic

Choreography by @benoitrichaud 
Musical arrangement by @cedric__tour

node.text:
So grateful to have worked with @benoitrichaud on two more amazing programs for this season. I absolutely love them both and I can’t wait to show everyone what we’ve been creating. But until then, I’m excited to announce my free skate music this year will be Nuvole Bianche by Ludovico Einaudi and arranged by @cedric__tour ❤️

Stay tuned for my SP music 😉

📸: @belinda.films
